# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../timeline.rst:23
msgid "Timeline"
msgstr "Garis Waktu"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../timeline.rst:25
msgid ""
"The timeline is where your video comes together. You arrange clips, trim "
"them, layer visuals, and make timing decisions here. If you are new to "
"editing, think of the timeline as a simple left-to-right story: earlier "
"moments on the left, later moments on the right."
msgstr ""
"Garis waktu adalah tempat video Anda disusun. Anda mengatur klip, "
"memotongnya, menumpuk visual, dan membuat keputusan waktu di sini. Jika Anda "
"baru dalam pengeditan, anggap garis waktu sebagai cerita sederhana dari kiri "
"ke kanan: momen awal di kiri, momen berikutnya di kanan."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../timeline.rst:32
msgid ""
"If you are just getting started, read :ref:`quick_tutorial_ref` first, then "
"come back here for more detail. For a labeled breakdown of toolbar controls, "
"see :ref:`timeline_toolbar_ref`."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda baru memulai, baca :ref:`quick_tutorial_ref` terlebih dahulu, lalu "
"kembali ke sini untuk detail lebih lanjut. Untuk rincian kontrol toolbar "
"yang diberi label, lihat :ref:`timeline_toolbar_ref`."

